name: Kick Him When He’s Down
description:
“Kick Him When He’s Down”
Digital Drawing
4320 x 5411 px
2021

“KUDA”, previously drawn by Aglis Dhamar Hapsara / Illustremor, meets “Calamity”.
This artwork was created in a “Sketch Jamming” initiated by Kuda Lari Collective (Semarang, Indonesia), in May 2021.
